Note 1: A Procedure Step State of SCHEDULED shall be supplied.
Note 2: Code Value for the Scheduled Station Name shall contain the string used to definitively match the TDD
instance with its representation on the TMS. It is not necessarily human-readable.
Note 3: Coding Scheme Designator for the Scheduled Station Name is a private coding scheme, and is not used explicitly in this profile.
Note 5: A reasonable date time range (such as the rest of the current day) shall be supplied to limit the size of the
returned result set. If operating in a mode where the patient 475 is selected on the TMS, the TMS is permitted to
over-filter the result set based upon this selection and return just the worklist items for the selected fraction.
Note: 11: Shall be empty.
